<title>THE BETTER LAND</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ginna mitin gam nuom ka mui,
 Lunggil kipaka ka gel tieng;
 A vak chun muntin a salhvak,
 A lopina vak hawihtak chun.

[V2]
 Hehpihna gam vak leh nawpna,
 Na vakin lei thim a nawhmang;
 Na mun galmuong chu chang ta'ng kau,
 Khuo a vaka thim a beih tieng.

[V3]
 2. Zie luigal nuomtak mai achun,
 Thimna leh buokna um talo;
 Kikhen sate kituok khawm ding,
 Ziechun kikhen um ta puo'n a.

[V4]
 3. Zie mun chuh lei mun bang ei puoi,
 Vakna chitin chuh a zam vel;
 Zan thim dahum na nawhmang di'n,
 Nisa vakte a ngai ta puoi.

[V5]
 4. Lungkhamna huihpi nung talo,
 Muonna leh nawpna mun achun;
 Vakvaite'n chawlhna mu ta'n au,
 Pathien pielgal mun nuom achun.</lyrics>
</song>